  "itineraryNotes": "TODO: consider SeaTac parking vs uber\n\nGay’s picks for hotels:\n\nFor your travel project, we need a hotel to take Hudson for school. I looked at a few hotels though the amex website and these are all acceptable to me but I figured you could book and use your app.  Acceptable\n\n[Hideaway](https://www.kirkwoodcollection.com/hideaway/rooms/)\n[Canary Hotel](https://www.ihg.com/kimptonhotels/hotels/us/en/canary-hotel-santa-barbara-ca/sabcn/hoteldetail)\n[The Stewared](https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/sbatx-the-steward-santa-barbara-a-tribute-portfolio-hotel/overview/)\n[Hotel Californian](https://www.hotelcalifornian.com/)\n\nI think we should arrive on the 17th of sept, run our purchase errands on the 18th and pick up supplies and then we are moving in on the 19th & 20th.  He will get a staggered time for move in on one of those dates? So I supposed we can fly home late on the 20th pretty safely?"
